Class Summary
Flickr Main entry point for the Flickrj API.
Parameter Class encapsulating a name/value parameter.
ParameterAlphaComparator Compare Parameter sorting on the key in alphabetical order.
ProxyAuthenticator Used to set the credentials for proxy-authentication in REST.setProxy(String, int, String, String).
RequestContext A thread local variable used to hold contextual information used in requests.
REST Transport implementation using the REST interface.
RESTResponse Flickr Response object.
SearchResultList<E> Search result list with additional meta data.
Transport The abstract Transport class provides a common interface for transporting requests to the Flickr servers.
 

Exception Summary
FlickrException Exception which wraps a Flickr error.
